@startmindmap
* Cardano contract security
** Removed by the eUTXO model
*** Reentrancy impossible (atomic tx)
*** Double-spend prevented by ledger
*** Determinism kills MEV / front-running
*** Native assets share ledger security
** Vulnerabilities that remain
*** Double satisfaction
*** Datum hijacking / arbitrary datum
*** Token forgery (one-shot, other-name)
*** Missing UTXO authentication
*** Time handling (interval bounds)
*** Resource exhaustion (unbounded value/datum/inputs)
*** Insufficient staking control
*** Other redeemer / missed input
** Defensive patterns
*** State / beacon token
*** Value-preservation check
*** Datum-continuity validation
*** Deadline via validity range
*** Minimal on-chain logic
** Verification (defense in depth)
*** Unit tests
*** Property-based testing
*** Professional audit
*** Formal verification
@endmindmap
